data.description: A Must SEE: Like New, One Owner Well Kept, Spacious Four Bedroom Three Bathroom Estate Home in professionally maintained Northbridge Estates Subdivision. This home features a rocking chair front porch and huge rear deck, awaiting family gatherings and entertainment. Kitchen has premium cabinetry, large island, solid counters, backsplash and luxury vinyl flooring for easy maintenance. Huge Owners Suite with separate tub and shower, plus many more amenities. Enjoy Fishing within minutes at Clayton County's JW Smith Reservoir & Park.  Preferred Lender EMG Mortgage, and Southeast Title Corp, Closing Attorney.
